						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">blargg wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">You're dealing with the fundamental problem of two masters: the frame rate and sample rate. You're going to have to slave one to the other (work this out on paper until you can see that there's no way around this).</div>
